      Constructs an AppointmentOutcome object with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      outcomeId - The unique identifier for the outcome.
      appointmentId - The unique identifier for the related appointment.
      date - The date of the outcome.
      serviceType - The type of service provided during the appointment (e.g., "Consultation", "Treatment").
      prescribedMedication - The medication prescribed during the appointment.
      medicationStatus - The status of the prescribed medication (e.g., "Pending", "Dispensed").
      consultationNotes - Additional notes from the consultation or appointment.
